{"id":"cli/build","title":"ng build","contents":"\n<article>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/build\", \"name\": \"build\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-build\">ng build<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/build#ng-build\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    <p>將 Angular 應用程式或庫編譯到給定輸出路徑處名為 dist/ 的輸出目錄中。</p>\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng <span class=\"cli-name\">build</span> [<var>project</var>]\n</code-example>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng <span class=\"cli-name\">b</span> [<var>project</var>]\n</code-example>\n\n\n\n    \n    <h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"----------mode_edit--code--------描述----\">\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/build/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/refs/heads/main/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/build/long-description.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n        描述\n    </h2>\n    <p>該命令可用於建構“應用程式”或“庫”型別的專案。當用於建構庫時，會呼叫不同的建構器，並且僅應用<code>ts-config</code>、<code>configuration</code>和<code>watch</code>選項。所有其他選項僅適用於建構應用程式。</p>\n<p>應用程式建構器使用 <a href=\"https://webpack.js.org/\">Webpack</a> 建構工具，可以在工作區配置檔案 ( <code>angular.json</code> ) 中指定預設配置選項或使用命名的替代配置。預設情況下，當你使用 CLI 建立專案時會建立一個<code>development</code> 配置，你可以透過指定 <code>--configuration development</code> 來使用該配置。</p>\n<p>配置選項通常對應於命令選項。你可以透過在命令列中指定相應的選項來覆蓋單個配置預設值。該命令可以接受以 dash-case 或 camelCase 給出的選項名稱。請注意，在配置檔案中，你必須以 camelCase 指定名稱。</p>\n<p>某些附加選項只能透過配置檔案設定，可以透過直接編輯或使用<code>ng config</code>命令來完成。其中包括 <code>assets</code>、<code>styles</code> 和 <code>scripts</code> 物件，它們提供了要包含在專案中的執行時全域資源。CSS 中的資源，例如圖像和字型，會在輸出資料夾的根目錄自動寫入並新增指紋。</p>\n<p>有關更多詳細資訊，請參閱<a href=\"guide/workspace-config\">工作區配置</a>。</p>\n\n    \n\n    \n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"arguments\">引數</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th style=\"width:15%\">引數</th>\n      <th style=\"width:40%\">說明</th>\n      <th>值型別</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">project</code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p>要建構的專案名。可以是應用或庫。</p>\n\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">選項</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th style=\"width:15%\">選項</th>\n    <th style=\"width:40%\">說明</th>\n    <th>值型別</th>\n    <th>預設值</th>\n  </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--allowed-common-js-dependencies</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>允許在沒有建構期警告的前提下使用的 CommonJS 軟體包列表。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">array</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--aot</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>使用預先編譯模式進行建構。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--base-href</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>正在建構的應用程式的 base URL。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--build-optimizer</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>使用 'aot' 選項時啟用高階建構最佳化。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--common-chunk</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>產生一個單獨的捆綁套件，其中包含跨多個捆綁套件使用的程式碼。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--configuration</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>以逗號分隔列表形式表示的一個或多個命名建構器配置，在 angular.json 的 <code>configurations</code> 部分指定。建構器使用命名配置來執行給定的目標。有關更多資訊，請參閱<a href=\"https://angular.io/guide/workspace-config#alternate-build-configurations\">https://angular.io/guide/workspace-config#alternate-build-configurations</a>。</p>\n\n      <p><span class=\"cli-aliases\">別名:</span> -c</p>\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--cross-origin</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>定義提供 CORS 支援的元素的 crossorigin 屬性設定。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">none | anonymous | use-credentials</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">none</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--delete-output-path</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在建構之前，刪除輸出路徑。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link deprecated-api-item\">--deploy-url</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      \n      <p><strong>已棄用：</strong></p>\n      <p translation-result=\"on\">檔案將部署到的 URL。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use \"baseHref\" option, \"APP_BASE_HREF\" DI token or a combination of both instead. For more information, see <a href=\"https://angular.io/guide/deployment#the-deploy-url\">https://angular.io/guide/deployment#the-deploy-url</a>.</p>\n\n      \n      \n      \n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--extract-licenses</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>將所有許可證（license）提取到一個單獨的檔案中。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--help</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在控制檯顯示關於本命令的幫助資訊。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--i18n-duplicate-translation</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>如何處理 i18n 的重複翻譯。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">warning | error | ignore</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">warning</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--i18n-missing-translation</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>i18n 要如何處理缺失翻譯。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">warning | error | ignore</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">warning</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--index</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>配置應用程式的 index.html 的產生方式。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--inline-style-language</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>用於應用程式的內聯元件樣式的樣式表語言。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">css | less | sass | scss</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">css</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--localize</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在一個或多個語言環境下翻譯這些套件。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--main</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>應用程式主入口點的完整路徑。是相對於當前工作空間的。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--named-chunks</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>對於延遲載入的塊，使用檔名進行命名。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--ngsw-config-path</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>ngsw-config.json 的路徑。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--optimization</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>啟用建構輸出的最佳化。包括指令碼和樣式的最小化、搖樹最佳化、消除死程式碼、內聯關鍵 CSS 和內聯字型等。欲知詳情，請參閱<a href=\"https://angular.cn/guide/workspace-config#optimization-configuration\">https://angular.cn/guide/workspace-config#optimization-configuration</a>。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--output-hashing</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>定義輸出檔名的快取無效雜湊（cache-busting hashing）的模式。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">none | all | media | bundles</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">none</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--output-path</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>新輸出目錄的完整路徑，是相對於當前工作空間的。預設情況下，會將輸出寫入當前專案中名為 dist/ 的資料夾。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--poll</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>啟用並定義檔案監視的輪詢間隔（以毫秒為單位）。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">number</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--polyfills</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>要包含進本建構中的Polyfill指令碼。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--preserve-symlinks</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>當解析模組時，不要使用真實路徑。如果未設定，則如果 NodeJS 啟用了 --preserve-symlinks 選項，就預設為 <code>true</code>。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--progress</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在建構時將進度記錄到控制檯。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--resources-output-path</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>放置樣式資源的路徑，是相對於 outputPath 的。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--service-worker</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在生產環境建構中產生 Service Worker 配置。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--source-map</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>輸出指令碼和樣式的原始碼對映資訊。欲知詳情，請參閱<a href=\"https://angular.cn/guide/workspace-config#source-map-configuration\">https://angular.cn/guide/workspace-config#source-map-configuration</a>。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--stats-json</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>產生一個 “stats.json” 檔案，可以使用 “webpack-bundle-analyzer” 之類別的工具進行分析。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--subresource-integrity</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>啟用子資源完整性驗證。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--ts-config</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>TypeScript 配置檔案相對於當前工作空間的完整路徑。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--vendor-chunk</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>產生僅包含供應商庫的單獨捆綁套件。此選項只能用於開發階段以縮短增量編譯的時間。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--verbose</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>將更多詳細資訊新增到輸出日誌記錄。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--watch</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>當檔案更改時自動建構。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--web-worker-ts-config</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>Web Worker 模組的 TypeScript 配置。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/enableProdMode\n - api/core/isDevMode\n - cli\n - guide/aot-compiler\n - guide/browser-support\n - guide/deployment\n - guide/i18n-common-deploy\n - guide/i18n-common-merge\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\n - guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale\n - guide/service-worker-getting-started\n - guide/what-is-angular\n - guide/workspace-config\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - cli/build#ng-build\n - guide/workspace-config\n - https://angular.cn/guide/workspace-config#optimization-configuration\n - https://angular.cn/guide/workspace-config#source-map-configuration\n - https://angular.io/guide/deployment#the-deploy-url\n - https://angular.io/guide/workspace-config#alternate-build-configurations\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/build/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/refs/heads/main/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/build/long-description.md\n - https://webpack.js.org/\n-->"}